      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon",
      "notes": "to taste"
    },
    {
      "name": "kanten agar water mixture",
      "amount": "1 cup",
      "notes": "cooled to 80 degrees fahrenheit"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "mix kanten agar powder and cassava flour in a bowl, set aside.",
    "heat coconut oil in a small saucepan over low heat.",
    "add unsalted butter to the saucepan and stir until melted.",
    "add tandoor spice mix and stir for 1 minute.",
    "add lime juice and stir for 2 minutes.",
    "add chopped cilantro, minced onion, and minced garlic to the saucepan and stir for 2 minutes.",
    "add sea salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "pour the saucepan mixture over the kanten agar powder mixture in the bowl and stir until combined.",
    "add the cooled kanten agar water mixture to the bowl and stir until combined.",
    "pour the mixture into a lined or greased 8-inch skillet or cake pan.",
    "refrigerate for at least 4 hours or overnight.",
    "to serve, invert the skillet or cake pan onto a plate and slice into wedges."
  ],
